        "rendered": "<p>Matt Helm I have been a research assistant in the Interactive Measurement Group (IMG) since spring 2018. My research and leadership tasks have changed every semester. In summer 2018, I became an action editor (for this very newsletter), and in fall 2018 I become a teaching assistant for Kim Barchard’s introductory statistics course. The following [&hellip;]</p>\n",
